text: William Churchill (1627–1702), of Colliton House, Dorchester and Muston Manor, Piddlehinton, Dorset, was an English politician. He married Grace Meller, the daughter of MP, John Meller. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Dorchester in 1685.http://www.historyofparliamentonline.org/volume/1660-1690/member/churchill- william-1627-1702 ==References== Category:1627 births Category:1702 deaths Category:English MPs 1685–1687 Category:Members of the Parliament of England for Dorchester
